His first familiy name is "Agirregabiria". Since it is a Basque family name, it should be written in the Basque orthographic convention, that is, it should be written "Agirregabiria" instead of "Aguirregabiria". Therefore, I changed all the "Aguirregabiria" variants to "Agirregabiria". I follow Euskaltzaindia, the Basque Royal Academy (http://www.euskaltzaindia.eus/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=4169&Itemid=805&lang=en).
